      "zh": "USP .45",
      "en": "USP .45"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "HK USP（“通用自动手枪”）手枪是一款用于替代HK P7系列手枪的新产品。它被公认为是准确、可靠的手枪。",
      "en": "The HK USP (Universelle Selbstladepistole - \"Universal Self-loading Pistol\") pistol is a further replacement of the HK P7 series pistols. Internationally accepted as an accurate and ultra-reliable handgun. Using a modified Browning-type action with a special patented recoil reduction system, the USP recoil reduction system reduces recoil effects on pistol components and also lowers the recoil forces felt by the shooter. This particular variant is chambered in .45 ACP. Manufactured by Heckler & Koch."
    },
